## Installation

### Clone the Repository

```bash
git clone https://github.com/Joy-maker-AI/lifepilot-ai.git
```

### Navigate to Project Folder

```bash
cd lifepilot-ai
```

### Install Frontend Dependencies

```bash
cd frontend
npm install
```

### Start Frontend

```bash
npm start
```

### Setup Backend

Open a new terminal:

```bash
cd backend
npm install
```

### Start Backend Server

```bash
node server.js
```

---

## Environment Variables

Create a `.env` file inside the backend folder and add:

```env
OPENAI_API_KEY=your_api_key
```
